            <title>[PIG-604] Kill the Pig job should kill all associated Hadoop Jobs</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/PIG-604</link>
                <project id="12310730" key="PIG">Pig</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Current if we kill the pig job on the client machine, those hadoop jobs already launched still keep running. We have to kill these jobs manually.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
